               </msIdentifier>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>Example of a collection of abstracts of contracts, compiled at local records office, in Ptolemaic times, most apparently refering to the 125th-26th year of Euergetes I. Also included ar leases of cleruchic land in the division of Themistes, abstracts of loans, short accounts, dowries and marriage contracts, sales of fruit and grape gardens, vineyards.</summary>
                  <msItemStruct>
                     <note type="general">Verso unpublished</note>
                     <note type="general">Margins: top, 1.1 cm.; bottom, 0.2 cm.</note>
                     <note type="local_note">1030, 1031, 1032, 2030, 2031, 2032, 2034, 2035, 2036, 2037, 2038, 2039</note>
                     <note type="local_note">Bancroft Library, Univ. of Calif., Berkeley</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">Greek</textLang>
                  </msItemStruct>
               </msContents>
